$ON_ZSHOWGRP
Onevent BEFORE_AREA Gosub AV_ZSHOWGRP From W1PJMSNP0
Return

$AV_ZSHOWGRP
Call LECTEXTRA(zc,"ATABDIV","LNGDES","388",num$([M]SHOWGRP(indice))) From ATEXTRA
